{
  "stem": "8947.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we heard that she tried to put that hut on fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But she didn't manage to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She was a psychopath.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were psychopaths.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "See, many of these SS guards-- I'm telling you, they were psychopaths.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had a license to kill and to torture you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think at least two days, or three.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were marching.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- and-- and we got weaker and weaker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally, we had-- it was 30 kilometers, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived to Bergen-Belsen in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was pitch dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got into the camps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I felt a terrible smell of death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was familiar with the odor of death.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I thought that probably they are going to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was like a craze, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people formed columns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some people were pushed into some barracks by these guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were hardly any place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The people were screaming outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was at the end of the column.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Finally, there was no place-- no way that you could put more people in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they said, well, rest of us who are out there, we had to-- we had to sleep right on the ground, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when morning came, you know, the ground of Bergen-Belsen was littered with corpses, of all stages of decay.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was seeing where we slept, next to the corpses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In front of me there were some pyramid of dead, where-- where the bodies were stripped of clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We called the Pyramid of Dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were hoisted up, you know, in a shape of a pyramid-- and that horrible corpses, of all stages of decay.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we-- all the time in Bergen-Belsen, three weeks was your life expectancy there.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
